- Add AnalysisReport DB model linked to user (stores full JSON result + summary fields)
- Modify analyze-csv endpoint to save report after analysis
- Add GET /api/reports (list user's reports), GET /api/reports/:id, DELETE /api/reports/:id
- Add listReports, getReport, deleteReport to frontend API layer
- Rewrite DashboardPage with report history sidebar (view old, upload new, delete)
- UploadAnalysisPanel now accepts savedReport prop for read-only viewing
- Each report is independent — no overlap between analyses

Co-Authored-By: PRAJITH VELLINGIRI 25CSR213 <prajithvellingiri.25cse@kongu.edu>
